hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted prescriptioncard.org reviews The standards developed by the industry and now enforceable by NERC have been “major strides” for the industry and “required everybody to step up their game,” said David Cook, NERC senior legal counsel, who 10 years ago was general counsel for NERC. Cook said he remembers sitting in his office — then in Princeton, N.J. — and watching the lights dim off and on a few times before eventually remaining on. Eventually, he and his colleagues found out what was occurring to the electric grid in eight states.
